Package: stepFCBF
Title: Fast Correlation Based Filter for Feature Selection: 'tidymodels' Recipe Step Integration
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Rowan", "Jacques-Hamilton", , "rowan.jacques.hamilton@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2945-472X"))
Description: Provides the step_FCBF function, which conducts  fast correlation based filter selection 
             within a 'tidymodels' recipe. step_FCBF uses the bioconductor 'FCBF' package as the engine,
             and integrates it within the 'tidymodels' framework.
